{"tha-ap37:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap37:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap37:0.3":"Mogharajattheraapadana ","tha-ap37:1.1":"“Atthadassi tu bhagava, ","tha-ap37:1.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap37:1.3":"Bhikkhusanghaparibyulho, ","tha-ap37:1.4":"rathiyam patipajjatha. ","tha-ap37:2.1":"Sissehi samparivuto, ","tha-ap37:2.2":"gharamha abhinikkhamim; ","tha-ap37:2.3":"Nikkhamitvanaham tattha, ","tha-ap37:2.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap37:3.1":"Abhivadiya sambuddham, ","tha-ap37:3.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap37:3.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap37:3.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap37:4.1":"Yavata rupino satta, ","tha-ap37:4.2":"arupi va asannino; ","tha-ap37:4.3":"Sabbe te tava nanamhi, ","tha-ap37:4.4":"anto honti samogadha. ","tha-ap37:5.1":"Sukhumacchikajalena, ","tha-ap37:5.2":"udakam yo parikkhipe; ","tha-ap37:5.3":"Ye keci udake pana, ","tha-ap37:5.4":"antojale bhavanti te. ","tha-ap37:6.1":"Yesanca cetana atthi, ","tha-ap37:6.2":"rupino ca arupino; ","tha-ap37:6.3":"Sabbe te tava nanamhi, ","tha-ap37:6.4":"anto honti samogadha. ","tha-ap37:7.1":"Samuddharasimam lokam, ","tha-ap37:7.2":"andhakarasamakulam; ","tha-ap37:7.3":"Tava dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap37:7.4":"kankhasotam taranti te. ","tha-ap37:8.1":"Avijjanivute loke, ","tha-ap37:8.2":"andhakarena otthate; ","tha-ap37:8.3":"Tava nanamhi jotante, ","tha-ap37:8.4":"andhakara padhamsita. ","tha-ap37:9.1":"Tuvam cakkhusi sabbesam, ","tha-ap37:9.2":"mahatamapanudano; ","tha-ap37:9.3":"Tava dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap37:9.4":"nibbayati bahujjano. ","tha-ap37:10.1":"Putakam purayitvana, ","tha-ap37:10.2":"madhukhuddamanelakam; ","tha-ap37:10.3":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap37:10.4":"upanesim mahesino. ","tha-ap37:11.1":"Patigganhi mahaviro, ","tha-ap37:11.2":"sahatthena maha isi; ","tha-ap37:11.3":"Bhunjitva tanca sabbannu, ","tha-ap37:11.4":"vehasam nabhamuggami. ","tha-ap37:12.1":"Antalikkhe thito sattha, ","tha-ap37:12.2":"atthadassi narasabho; ","tha-ap37:12.3":"Mama cittam pasadento, ","tha-ap37:12.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap37:13.1":"‘Yenidam thavitam nanam, ","tha-ap37:13.2":"buddhasettho ca thomito; ","tha-ap37:13.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap37:13.4":"duggatim so na gacchati. ","tha-ap37:14.1":"Catuddasancakkhattum so, ","tha-ap37:14.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap37:14.3":"Pathabya rajjam atthasatam, ","tha-ap37:14.4":"vasudham avasissati. ","tha-ap37:15.1":"Panceva satakkhattunca, ","tha-ap37:15.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap37:15.3":"Padesarajjam asankheyyam, ","tha-ap37:15.4":"mahiya karayissati. ","tha-ap37:16.1":"Ajjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap37:16.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap37:16.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap37:16.4":"sasane pabbajissati. ","tha-ap37:17.1":"Gambhiram nipunam attham, ","tha-ap37:17.2":"nanena vicinissati; ","tha-ap37:17.3":"Mogharajati namena, ","tha-ap37:17.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap37:18.1":"Tihi vijjahi sampannam, ","tha-ap37:18.2":"katakiccamanasavam; ","tha-ap37:18.3":"Gotamo satthavahaggo, ","tha-ap37:18.4":"etadagge thapessati’. ","tha-ap37:19.1":"Hitva manusakam yogam, ","tha-ap37:19.2":"chetvana bhavabandhanam; ","tha-ap37:19.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap37:19.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap37:20.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap37:20.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap37:20.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap37:21.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mogharajo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap37:22.1":"Mogharajattherassapadanam pancamam. "}